<HEAD>Anniversaries of Wall Opening and Crystal Night; Gorbachev Visits</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Subs grafs 11-14, `Jochen Feilcke...' to CLARIFY news
conference by Schabowski was taped last year. Pickup 15th graf pvs,
